I think about Saturday and we're going to have more time, it's really great."
The training camp ends with UCLA stopping training. This is not an easy task, given the clear line of sight in the adjacent parking lot and the Luskin Center. The Luskin Center Premium Hotel has been bruised by football thrown through the guard net behind the goalposts.
