Will China fall behind if China does not build this type of warship?
With the recent world's major naval powers have announced the construction plan of the new frigate, as if overnight the frigate has become the focus of attention of the major powers of the navy, first of all Japan in the 2018 annual defense budget to determine the purchase of two new frigates, so that the Japanese DEX frigate plan finally has a substantial breakthrough, and then the United States Lockheed Martin recently announced the latest plan of the US FPG frigate plan, so where should China's new frigate go?
With the launch of a new 054A frigate at the end of 2017, marking that the 054A frigate has built up to 29 ships, has approached the sum of the 053H series frigates, and from the first 054A launched in 2006, the construction process of 054A has been 12 years, even in the world, the construction of so many high-performance general-purpose frigates, in addition to China, only the United States in the 7th and 80s of the last century built the "Perry" frigate can be compared.
The reason why so many 054As was built is simple: affordable, easy to use, and supplement the Navy owes for years.
054A frigate with high cost performance and good combat effectiveness for many years by the Chinese Navy's favor, its displacement of about 4000 tons, equipped with a 76 mm main gun, 32 units of sea red flag -16 and fish-8 anti-submarine missile launch a common hair system, 8 eagle strikes 83 and a straight-9 helicopter, although it was built in 2006, the design time is very early a kind of ship, but its combat effectiveness even in today's is not too bad, looking at the world's frigates.
But after all, this is a type of ships designed in the early 21st century, the weapon configuration is set aside, its power system and electronic radar equipment compared with the current world's mainstream frigates already have a big gap, like Europe's same type of frigate has been equipped with full electric propulsion, small multi-functional phased array radar, large size helicopter deck, but also to develop a new model.
So how China's new frigate should be developed is directly related to its future positioning and the strategic direction of our navy.
The future development of the Chinese Navy will surely become a blue-water navy, and the future will also be to the ocean, with the rapid deployment of areas where China's vital interests are closely related, the display of force, and the ability to have a strong combat power to ensure that China's vital interests in the region are not damaged, so it seems that the new Hu Weijiang will move towards large-scale and oceanic development.
Looking at the positioning problem of the new frigate in the future Chinese naval sequence, the future Chinese Navy should be similar to the US Navy, except for the necessary offshore defense ships, other main ships will form an aircraft carrier battle group or amphibious assault ship strike group according to the needs of the situation.
The role of the new frigate in the future aircraft carrier battle group should serve as anti-submarine main force and the positioning of the near-area clearance, in the amphibious assault ship strike group should serve as a escort ship class, then according to such demand, the new frigate must have a strong anti-submarine capability and a good medium-range area clearance capability.
Based on the above positioning, it is possible to boldly imagine the approximate appearance of domestic frigates in the future.
First of all, the displacement relative to the current 054A frigate will have a substantial increase, it is estimated that the displacement of the new frigate will reach about 5000-6000 tons; the power system will use a QC280 improved gas turbine and two diesel engines composed of an integrated electric propulsion system, the maximum speed is expected to reach about 30 knots, the endurance will also be greatly increased; as for the weapon configuration 76 mm main gun and 1130 near-arm gun should be retained, but will add a red flag 10 launch system, the main gun should have a 32-48 rear.A large 8-16 unit vertical hair system should be installed for launching eagle strike 18 and new cruise missiles; the hangar and shutdown platform will also be increased to accommodate and store two 10-ton helicopters; as for electronic radar systems, high-end should be equipped with small four-sided fixed phased array radar based on the development of the 346A, and can use multi-functional rotating phased array radar similar to the European frigate.
In this way, the overall level of the new frigate will reach the current world-class level, even compared with the United States FFG.
Of course, the above concept is only the author's conjecture on the domestic new frigate, how we can only wait until the new frigate is launched to find out, let us look forward to it together.
